snippet.title: Meghan Markle Denies Kate Middleton Diss Over Birth Certificate
snippet.description:
After Meghan Markle shut down tabloid claims that she removed her name from Archie's birth certificate as a diss towards Kate Middleton, Graeme O'Neil and Keshia Chante discuss during "ET Canada Live".
